# radroots-log

Tracing-based logging primitives for the Rad Roots SDK runtime crates.

## Goals

- define stable logging and initialization primitives for shared runtime use
- support std and no_std targets with deterministic behavior across environments
- provide consistent tracing integration for Rad Roots crate consumers
- keep logging setup reusable across application and service surfaces

